videos.headline: UCF picks up first TD of game
videos.description: UCF's Taj McGowan runs into the end zone for a 2-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: White puts Memphis in the lead with 11-yd TD
videos.description: Brady White runs 11 yards into the end zone to give the Tigers a 10-7 lead over the Knights.

videos.headline: Henderson widens Memphis' lead with 25-yd TD run
videos.description: Darrell Henderson keeps the Tigers moving with a 25-yard touchdown run to put Memphis up 17-7.

videos.headline: UCF's Milton connects with Davis for 75-yd TD
videos.description: McKenzie Milton finds Gabriel Davis, who sprints down the field for a 75-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Pollard continues the Memphis run with 19-yd TD
videos.description: Tony Pollard widens the gap for Memphis with a 19-yard touchdown run to make the score 30-14.

videos.headline: McGowan gets UCF back in the game with 71-yd TD run
videos.description: Taj McGowan sprints down the field into the end zone for a 71-yard Knights touchdown.

videos.headline: Memphis falls to UCF by one in dramatic end
videos.description: Down 31-30 with 15 seconds left, Brady White finds Tony Pollard for 9 yards, but time runs out and Memphis loses to UCF.
